{"tid":2479271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東江縱隊　在香港打家劫舍　屠殺神父天主教徒　犯下不少戰爭罪行","createTime":"2021-04-07T16:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T17:27:48.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d658b6fa1b636f94c72a2eb855e3a5e2a7ea97d","tid":2479271,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/94802341615/posts/10154323395806616/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F94802341615%2Fposts%2F10154323395806616%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=e5cb513d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/94802341615/posts/10154323395806616/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcVePjMGgYkrun3rGYzLAQr8RcmuS246JVGB3FJgtACMB?filename=AARZS6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAARZS6s.jpg&h=8e95b922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：LadyKylie in Germany<br />\n<br />\n中國常在97後的主流媒體說到二戰時的共產黨小隊「東江」縱隊是香港守軍主力似的，事實守軍是由英聯邦國家（英軍、加軍、英藉印軍等）加上本地香港義勇軍等組成的萬多人，迎戰幾萬精鋭日軍。<br />\n<br />\n東江迎救英美戰俘主要為收集情報，而在淪陷後只打過一些遊撃戰，不是主力軍，卻也犯下不少戰爭罪行，新界居民說「遊撃隊」打家劫舍，而在西貢對幾位神父和天主教徒的屠殺，有留意歷史的朋友也該略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n所以梅窩事件也應作個紀錄。"},{"pid":"0cbd322c24154a92efafa277a5c4021e4ff39e27","tid":2479271,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"咪作大啦，基本上香港日軍被東江蹤隊全滅咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e407650d07e3005219183f4080a94b84649bce8","tid":2479271,"uid":143400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbd322c24154a92efafa277a5c4021e4ff39e27","tid":2479271,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"咪作大啦，基本上香港日軍被東江蹤隊全滅咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"真 聽講個幾粒核彈都係佢地偷今地潛入美軍總部射的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br